    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This beautiful throne is delicately crafted from pale stone carved  with images of dancing nymphs and frolicking satyrs. A throne of pleasing mien imparts its continuous heroism effect to anyone seated upon it. A creature that bows or otherwise offers fealty to anyone sitting upon the throne (regardless of whether the person is a rightful ruler or not) gains a +2 circumstance bonus on Charisma-based skill checks and a +1 morale bonus on Will saving throws for 24 hours.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, eagle's splendor, heroism, resistance</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Heroes Of The High Court",
